WHITE RIVER – The Cansa Lowveld Galito’s Golf Day took place last Friday at White River Country Club. Ninety-two players, in teams of four, spent the day on the course, all in the name of a good cause.  Cansa Socialite winner in the 13 to 19 years category, Bajabulise Thela was on hand, rallying participants to buy tickets for the lucky draw in which amazing prizes were up for grabs.  Albert Booysen and Hans Miljou were the winners, followed by Ronald Ncube and Vuyile Resha and Mark Rocher and Brian Hogg in second and third place respectively.
A total of R50 000 was raised on the day.